**JavaScript**
JavaScript.jobs is a niche job board dedicated specifically to JavaScript-related roles, covering technologies like Node.js, React, Angular, Vue, Next.js, and TypeScript.
It connects developers with companies hiring for frontend, backend, and full-stack positions, including remote, contract, and full-time opportunities.
The platform is mainly used by JavaScript developers to find focused, high-relevance job listings without filtering through unrelated roles.

Link: https://javascript.jobs/

