**Jobright**
Jobright AI – AI job search platform
 is an AI‑driven job search tool that matches your experience to relevant listings, tailors resumes, autofills applications, and helps you track or network your way to interviews.
It pulls from millions of jobs, uses AI to score fit and reduce manual work, and aims to speed up the job hunt process.
Some users love how fast it surfaces roles and customizes applications, but like any aggregator, you should still verify listings and details yourself.
Link: https://jobright.ai/

